title: #66: Shitbag (Johnny Pemberton)
itunes:title: Shitbag with Johnny Pemberton
description: Johnny Pemberton met me at the Comedy Store and we talked about his horribly sick colon. Most of us take going to the bathroom fof granted. Not Johnny. To him, every dump is a blessing. A smelly, smelly blessing.
